{
  "texts": [
    "However, integrating ML into plant molecular studies poses notable challenges.",
    "ML approaches, similar to traditional plant molecular methods, are highly contextspecific, underscoring the importance of meticulous experimental design.",
    "It's essential to recognize that while ML aims to create predictive models, each ML algorithm comes with distinct strengths and weaknesses, influencing predictive efficiency under specific conditions.",
    "Consequently, an ML model crafted for one dataset may struggle to generalize well to others due to inherent biological and technical variations.",
    "The abundance of omics datasets provides a treasure trove of information."
  ]
}